tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE financial_assets (
    asset_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    asset_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    asset_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    asset_value DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    purchase_date DATE NOT NULL,
    owner_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE stocks (
    symbol STRING PRIMARY KEY,
    name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    volume INT
)

CREATE TABLE bonds (
    issuer STRING PRIMARY KEY,
    type STRING,
    interest_rate DECIMAL,
    maturity_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE investments (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    asset_name TEXT,
    asset_type TEXT,
    quantity INT,
    value DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE stocks (
    stock_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    company_name TEXT,
    stock_symbol TEXT,
    shares INT,
    price DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE real_estate (
    property_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    street_address TEXT,
    city TEXT,
    country TEXT,
    price DECIMAL
);
